title: Miele Dishwashers: LED Lighting
description:
Miele Dishwashers: LED Lighting

BrillianLight, four powerful LED lights, immerse the entire dishwasher interior with light for easy loading and unloading. This feature is now available in both Lumen and Diamond models.
